function permgen (a, n) if n == 0 then coroutine.yield(a) else for i=1,n do
-- put i-th element as the last one a[n], a[i] = a[i], a[n]
-- generate all permutations of the other elements permgen(a, n - 1)
-- restore i-th element a[n], a[i] = a[i], a[n]
end end end
function perm (a) local n = table.getn(a) return coroutine.wrap(function () permgen(a, n) end) end
function printResult (a) for i,v in ipairs(a) do io.write(v, " ") end io.write("\n") end
for p in perm{"a", "b", "c"} do printResult(p) end
